{"tid":720970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實衛冕魔咒唔止係魔咒咁簡單","createTime":"2018-06-28T10:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T11:00:43.000Z","uid":110761,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee68e88a2665cb7dcec5429d6ed005263cca6fbc","tid":720970,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"歐洲足球四大強隊  德西意法無一倖免<br />\n全部小組賽玩完  其實係必然發生嘅定律<br />\n<br />\n教練會傾向用番上屆用嘅戰術同球員  因為上屆就係咁贏  但對面可以用四年時間研究同練習點破解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對球員嚟講  球員會覺得冠軍都拎埋無咩好博  而且上屆都係咁贏  今屆輕鬆出線啦 <br />\n但其它隊球員就覺得一世人可能得一次機會  斷腳都要踢  心態上已經輸哂 <br />\n<br />\n對隊波嚟講  大家對佢哋好大期望  要承受好大壓力  特別係自己國家嘅傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係... 唯一倖免嘅巴西不愧係足球王國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f9922f40ec11368f3bc75a088245bb0934374b","tid":720970,"uid":4213,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"廢文"},{"pid":"d9e6c9d78f37bc23fcc17205823ccc2dcab5f351","tid":720970,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢文</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea76192d3d81493cf218f3a6e33afa9b1d666981","tid":720970,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實個問題係心態<br />\n上屆贏左, 今屆無咁博, 無左團火<br />\n但其他隊隊同你博老命, 想盡辦法贏你<br />\n梗係好易比人踼走"},{"pid":"1cdf199377f23167854828b50645cc3aac90e72d","tid":720970,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"06巴西都柒啦，明星陣容輸比法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92b5651573f2dadb69b549b9bbae3f878863fb1","tid":720970,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"02年冠軍, 06年果屆巴西入左8強<br />\n但其實果時弱隊仲未興防守反擊, 泊大巴<br />\n<br />\n但之後果幾屆, 好多隊同你博, 利用戰術利用大巴利用防守, 加埋同你博<br />\n<br />\n所以小組出局"},{"pid":"e21a99ec5013db473bf0ebbd06f041432a04383c","tid":720970,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea76192d3d81493cf218f3a6e33afa9b1d666981","tid":720970,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實個問題係心態<br />\n上屆贏左, 今屆無咁博, 無左團火<br />\n但其他隊隊同你博老命, 想盡辦法贏你<br />\n梗係好易比人踼走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"琴晚德國去到70幾分鐘都仲係懶懶閒，唔講以為和都出線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3679ce9b9b27e2a45872f537d508e97f0db073","tid":720970,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"心態真係好重要, 德國尋日成班好似小花咁係度散步<br />\n泡菜係芧, 但睇得出有火"},{"pid":"07116a6f06a8f951c78ead2065cda4550e08f313","tid":720970,"uid":110761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21f9922f40ec11368f3bc75a088245bb0934374b","tid":720970,"uid":4213,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"廢文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"都唔係好廢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5e0eef91cf84331987c55e0d321155b3aa38bb","tid":720970,"uid":13929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"阿媽唔止係女人咁簡單<br />\n仲要一定唔係男人"},{"pid":"562649304fb06b44daed8164b3c94f5c0ea918b7","tid":720970,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"佢地心諗, 話晒我地係上屆冠軍<br />\n雖然唔好話贏到冠軍, 但過分組有咩難度?<br />\n<br />\n我估佢地心態係咁"},{"pid":"2e818917a4bc451eaace7e7d39bec5f17fe69191","tid":720970,"uid":23809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:00:43.000Z","msg":"山係石頭海係水"}]}